ygData.msgSnippet: Spare me man. And I m working on Sat. I might able to sneak in for a short while but can t play long. only 1 hour dinner break. And if want to go Upper Guk
ygData.messageBody:
Spare me man. And I'm working on Sat. I might able to sneak in for a short
while but can't play long. only 1 hour dinner break.
And if want to go Upper Guk then I bring my lvl 15th paladin along. At least can
heal and buff a little.
